				<li id="16535018" class="cmnt-root" data="54" data-d="1647679126000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t579598/Dragoncrest-Greatshield-Talisman" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">19 Mar 2022 04:38</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16535018" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Another way to understand it.<br/><br/>Normally you take 100% damage. With this, it reduces damage by 20% or 1-.2, meaning you take 80% damage.<br/><br/><br/>When stacked with something else, lets say your armor is a 30% reduction, that means you take 70%.<br/><br/><br/>So the result of these together is going to be .7*.8 for a result of .56 or 56% damage taken. The net result is 44% instead of the expected 50%.<br/><br/><br/>The reason it works like this is so that you can never achieve 100% damage reduction and therefore the more you invest into it, the less return you get.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16535018" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16535018" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">4</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>73</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>19</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16535018"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16535018" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16535018"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
